# Even Hub SDK

Before changing files in `src/even/`:

1. Consult official Even Hub documentation.
2. Inspect `node_modules/@evenrealities/even_hub_sdk/dist/index.d.ts` for the pinned version.
3. Never guess method names, event types, or payload shapes.

## Boundaries

- All `@evenrealities/even_hub_sdk` imports stay in `src/even/`.
- `src/app/` and `src/ui/` must not import the SDK.
- Future Hermes HTTP code goes in `src/hermes/`, not here.

## Event routing (verified)

- Taps, double-taps, lifecycle → `event.sysEvent`
- Scroll up/down → `event.textEvent`
- R1 vs G2 → `sysEvent.eventSource` (`EventSourceType`)
- Coalesce zero: `event.sysEvent?.eventType ?? 0`
- Double-tap → `shutDownPageContainer(1)` in both envelopes
- Cleanup on `SYSTEM_EXIT_EVENT` / `ABNORMAL_EXIT_EVENT`

## Conflicts

If docs and installed types disagree, note the conflict in code comments or PR description before changing behavior.

